{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"328","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"全球暖化加劇 北極「最後一塊冰層」破了！","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/0907.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 480px;' /><span style='color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;'>因全球暖化日益嚴重，北極最厚冰層於今年出現2次裂縫。圖擷自</span><a align='right' href='https://www.theguardian.com/world/2018/aug/21/arctics-strongest-sea-ice-breaks-up-for-first-time-on-record' style='color: rgb(0, 84, 166); text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; letter-spacing: 1px;' target='_blank'><font color='#0074ad'>《The Guardian》</font></a></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;'>隨著全球<a href='https://udn.com/search/tagging/2/%E6%9A%96%E5%8C%96' rel='109105' style='color: rgb(0, 84, 166); text-decoration-line: none; outline: none;'><span style='color: rgb(136, 136, 136); text-decoration-line: underline;'>暖化</span></a>日益加劇，各國也出現了許多氣候異常的現象，而「<a href='https://udn.com/search/tagging/2/%E5%8C%97%E6%A5%B5' rel='103938' style='color: rgb(0, 84, 166); text-decoration-line: none; outline: none;'><span style='color: rgb(136, 136, 136); text-decoration-line: underline;'>北極</span></a>最後一塊冰層」也在今年裂了2次，讓專家直呼：好可怕！</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;'>根據<a href='https://www.theguardian.com/world/2018/aug/21/arctics-strongest-sea-ice-breaks-up-for-first-time-on-record' style='color: rgb(0, 84, 166); text-decoration-line: none; outline: none;' target='_blank'>《The Guardian》</a>報導，全球最厚、最古老的北極海冰層在今年出現了二次鬆動，由於受到北半球的暖風與氣候變化的熱浪影響，該冰層早在今年2月時出現了裂縫，而平均為攝氏零下20度的北極，在上週竟出現了攝氏17度高溫以及風速11節強風，導致該冰層再次出現裂痕。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;'>該冰層位於格陵蘭島以北的水域，之所以會被稱為「北極的最後冰層」是因為該冰層厚度超過4米，如此厚實的冰通常不易移動，而且專家原先堅信該冰層能抵擋全球暖化的影響，成為堅持到最後的冰層，沒想到今年卻二度出現了裂痕。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;'>此現象讓不少氣象專家感到相當緊張，挪威氣象學者拉韋涅（Thomas Lavergne）分享了一張衛星偵測圖，圖上可見海水穿透了白色冰層，露出數百英里的格陵蘭海岸線，並用可怕來形容此現象，他表示因為融冰已經遠離海岸，恐將移動至南部更溫暖的海域。而丹麥氣象專員馬特拉姆（Ruth Mottram）則表示，格陵蘭島以北幾乎所有的冰都已經破碎。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/0907%202.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 562px;' /><span style='color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;'>1979～2018的北極海冰量。圖擷自《The Guardian》</span></p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/0907%203.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 803px;' /><span style='color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify;'>格陵蘭海岸線露出。圖擷自</span><a align='right' href='https://twitter.com/lavergnetho/status/1026727309921988608' style='color: rgb(0, 84, 166); text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; font-family: Meiryo, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑体, 微軟雅黑體, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Arial, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, 黑体, 黑體; letter-spacing: 1px;' target='_blank'><font color='#0074ad'>Twitter/Thomas Lavergne</font></a></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>資料來源:https://udn.com/news/story/6812/3326527</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2018-09-07","clk_count":"260"}},"__N_SSG":true}